features: The Package Includes - 120Pcs boho computer stationery paper in six different designs, they will offer sufficient quantity and choices to meet your various needs.

Cute Design - Our print paper featuring the boho theme, patterned with various colorful border including flower, sunset, hand, stone and heart, cute and delicate. While enrich the appearance of the paper, it also increase the fun and pleasant atmosphere.
Premium Material - Made of good quality paper, sturdy and durable, not easy to fade or tear, no peculiar smell and with long service time, it will offer you a comfortable using experience.
Large Size - Each computer stationery paper measures 21 x 27cm/ 8.5 x 11 inch, large enough to meet your different needs of printing and writing.

Wide Application - Our boho stationery paper can be applied in various occasions, great for adding text, pictures, drawings, and heartfelt messages, suitable for scrapbooking, card making, letter writing, invitations, and other paper crafts, favor for school and classroom.
